Flavour x Chidinma makes available their Ep which they titled “40yrs Everlasting“. It is a 5 track EP and off it we dish out the 3 track tagged “Mma Mma“, produced by Masterkraft. This song is about Love, a lady shooting her shot for the Man that makes her heart bang/beat differently. Chidinma sings for the single guy she wants to mingle with, while original Flavour comes in with the dance vibe. Sing along to ‘Mma Mma’, Dance, Enjoy and let us know in the comment section below about your view.   DOWNLOAD MP3 The post Flavour x Chidinma – “Mma Mma” appeared first on tooXclusive. Source: Too Xclusive